Class Summary
ET_GenericReceiver Push Notification Receiver, useful for catching all kinds of events and intents broadcast by Android.

ETGeofenceReceiver BroadcastReceiver to handle geofence triggered events.
ETLandingPagePresenter Simple activity to load a url into a webview and present it to the user.
ETLocationManager ETLocationManager is responsible for finding an accurate location and retrieving a list of geofences from ExactTarget.
